{"tid":1076474,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【歐國盃外圍賽】波蘭賽前爆流感　8將中招　元凶疑為前鋒米利克","createTime":"2019-03-25T01:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T06:08:46.000Z","uid":1121,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"feebb184b5caef1b596e37a9211199db015c0c72","tid":1076474,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:16:46.000Z","msg":"歐國盃外圍賽進行得如火如荼之際，G組波蘭隊卻爆發流感鬧兵荒。前鋒比亞迪克及米利克等最少8人中招，明晨迎戰拉脫維亞需抱病上陣。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭歐國外G組首仗作客險勝奧地利1：0，但中場施連斯基比賽撞傷背部，明晨上陣成疑。主帥比斯錫（Jerzy Brzeczek）賽前卻帶來更壞消息：「隊內爆發流感，一共有8名球員染病，包括比亞迪克。」他續指守將碧拿歷克和比列薩尼斯基昨日也沒操練，並歸咎於作客維也納時酒店的冷氣問題。<br />\n<br />\n不過比斯錫也提到最先有病徵的是米利克，而這名拿玻里前鋒有可能是帶菌者，因為其球會隊友法比安彭拿早前發燒送院，確診豬流感，因而退出西班牙隊。拿玻里門將阿歷斯美列特同樣因病未能為意大利U21上陣。"},{"pid":"17390fd4d779c42b5f7ee66eb87f34158b2a03a8","tid":1076474,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:17:33.000Z","msg":"廢鋒帶埋菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b5d68627b98a25ddcea5d0f0c4c97279dd37da","tid":1076474,"uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17390fd4d779c42b5f7ee66eb87f34158b2a03a8","tid":1076474,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:17:33.000Z","msg":"廢鋒帶埋菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />神鋒"},{"pid":"3f1c40e8cff016bdd54545c191bd8ebaef81884b","tid":1076474,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23b5d68627b98a25ddcea5d0f0c4c97279dd37da","tid":1076474,"uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17390fd4d779c42b5f7ee66eb87f34158b2a03a8","tid":1076474,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:17:33.000Z","msg":"廢鋒帶埋菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 